logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Build & Output Directories (For TypeScript or bundled applications)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
dist/
build/
out/
.next/

